                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Fox</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Quito</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-05-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 6, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Fox reports that Ecuador will be represented at the Second Peace Conference
                    by Señor Rendon, the Ecuadorean minister to France.)</p>
            </div>
